Class JvfsFileSystemProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.nio.file.spi.FileSystemProvider
      • de.weltraumschaf.jvfs.impl.JvfsFileSystemProvider

  • public final class JvfsFileSystemProvider
extends FileSystemProvider
    Implements the I/O operations. Inspired by implementation of sun.nio.fs.LinuxFileSystemProvider and ZipFS demo.

    Sven Strittmatter

      • checkUri

        void checkUri(URI uri)
        Checks URI against some rules. Rules:
        • the URI scheme matches getScheme()
        • the URI has no authority
        • the path is not null
        • the path component is the root directory
        • the URI has no query part
        • the URI has no fragment
        Throws IllegalArgumentException if any rule is not complied.
        Parameters:
        uri - must not be null
